tt v\u00e4lja l\u00e4ge f\u00f6r ljus- eller insynsavsk\u00e4rmningen.<\/p>\n<h3>H\u00e5llbar och smart funktion<\/h3>\n<p>Pliss\u00e9gardinen hissas och regleras med en kraftig draglina. En smart mekanism l\u00e5ser gardinen i det l\u00e4ge du vill ha den. Bellevue Solskydd kvalitetss\u00e4krar din pliss\u00e9gardin i egna lokaler f\u00f6re leverans \u2013 och montering, om du v\u00e4ljer den tj\u00e4nsten.<\/p>\n<h3>V\u00e4lj f\u00e4rg och material<\/h3>\n<p>Bellevue Solskydd erbjuder dig en m\u00e4ngd olika kvaliteter p\u00e5 v\u00e4v och i m\u00e5nga f\u00e4rger och nyanser. D\u00e4rf\u00f6r kan alltid f\u00e5 pliss\u00e9gardiner har helt matchar milj\u00f6 och \u00f6vrig inredning.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][\/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_2&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.16&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_image src=&#8221;https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/kostnadsfritt-hembesok-BTN.png&#8221; title_text=&#8221;kostnadsfritt hembeso\u0308k- BTN&#8221; url=&#8221;\/hem\/#hembasok\/&#8221; show_bottom_space=&#8221;off&#8221; align=&#8221;right&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.23&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; transform_translate=&#8221;30px|0px&#8221; transform_translate_linked=&#8221;off&#8221; transform_rotate=&#8221;0deg|0deg|10deg&#8221; position_origin_a=&#8221;center_center&#8221; position_origin_r=&#8221;bottom_right&#8221; width=&#8221;150px&#8221; width_tablet=&#8221;150px&#8221; width_phone=&#8221;120px&#8221; width_last_edited=&#8221;on|desktop&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;40px||||false|false&#8221; animation_style=&#8221;slide&#8221; animation_direction=&#8221;right&#8221; animation_duration=&#8221;1500ms&#8221; animation_intensity_slide=&#8221;30%&#8221; border_radii=&#8221;on|10px|10px|10px|10px&#8221; box_shadow_style=&#8221;preset3&#8243; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221; transform_styles__hover_enabled=&#8221;on|hover&#8221; transform_scale_