>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Vanliga fr\u00e5gor om pliss\u00e9gardiner<\/h3>\n<p>[\/et_pb_text][et_pb_accordion _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; custom_margin=&#8221;|||-3px||&#8221;][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Kan man f\u00e5 m\u00e5ttanpassade pliss\u00e9gardiner?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; open=&#8221;on&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243;]<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Pliss\u00e9gardinerna m\u00e5ttanpassas efter dina \u00f6nskem\u00e5l.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Erbjuder ni hembes\u00f6k?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; open=&#8221;off&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243;]<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Bellevue Solskydd erbjuder ett gratis hembes\u00f6k av en solskyddsexperter, som ger dig tips och r\u00e5d kring pliss\u00e9gardiner och hur det b\u00e4st passar ditt hem och dina \u00f6nskem\u00e5l.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kostnadsfritt hembes\u00f6k erbjuds under f\u00f6ruts\u00e4ttning av Bellevue Solskydd \u00e4r med genom hela processen, fr\u00e5n m\u00e5ttagning till montering. D\u00e5 har du som kund \u00e4ven fulla garantier, b\u00e5de p\u00e5 produkter och montering. <\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/#hembasok\/\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Boka ett gratis hembes\u00f6k!<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Ing\u00e5r montering av pliss\u00e9gardinerna?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi levererar och monterar de m\u00e5ttbest\u00e4llda\u200b pliss\u00e9gardinerna efter dina \u00f6nskem\u00e5l.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][et_pb_accordion_item title=&#8221;Vad kostar pliss\u00e9gardiner?&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.27.4&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; hover_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; sticky_enabled=&#8221;0&#8243; open=&#8221;off&#8221;]<\/p>\n<p>Priset p\u00e5 pliss\u00e9gardiner varierar beroende p\u00e5 val av v\u00e4v och m\u00e4ngd gardin. Vi str\u00e4var alltid efter att erbjuda h\u00f6gkvalitativa l\u00f6sningar till konkurrenskraftiga priser, som uppfyller dina behov och budget.<\/p>\n<p>F\u00f6r en mer exakt prisuppgift, rekommenderar vi att du<span>\u00a0<\/span><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https:\/\/bellevuesolskydd.se\/kontakt\/\">kontaktar oss<\/a><span>\u00a0<\/span>direkt f\u00f6r konsultation och en offert anpassad efter dina f\u00f6ruts\u00e4ttningar och \u00f6nskem\u00e5l.<\/p>\n<p>[\/et_pb_accordion_item][\/et_pb_accordion][\/et_pb_column][\/et_pb_row][\/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=&#8221;1&#8243; admin_label=&#8221;Services&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; custom_margin=&#8221;||||false|false&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;||||false|false&#8221; locked=&#8221;off&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_row column_structure=&#8221;1_3,1_3,1_3&#8243; use_custom_gutter=&#8221;on&#8221; gutter_width=&#8221;1&#8243; make_equal=&#8221;on&#8221; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.2&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; width=&#8221;100%&#8221; max_width=&#8221;1400px&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;0px||0px||true|false&#8221; global_colors_info=&#8221;{}&#8221;][et_pb_column type=&#8221;1_3&#8243; _builder_version=&#8221;4.22.1&#8243; _module_preset=&#8221;default&#8221; background_color=&#8221;#f4f3ef&#8221; custom_padding=&#8221;40px|20px|40px|20px|true|true&#8221; border_width_all=&#8221;12px&#8221; border_color_all=&#8221;rgba(0,0,0,0)&#8221; global_colors_inf